Name: Tc.OutboundSynchronisation.MaxRetries
Description: Retry mechanism configuration for doing calls to integration layer: value at specific index (identifies which retry call in sequence of retries is it) specifies time in minutes after previous failed call, when this retry should be executed

Name: Tc.Wr.SsoToken.ExpiredSecondsFromNow
Description: Seconds after which token is expired and should be rejected by wr web service

Name: Tc.Wr.SsoToken.NotBeforeTimeSecondsFromNow
Description: Seconds before which token should be rejected by wr web service
